      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BETTORS PRIDE (12) made it three wins on the trot when taking out the Winter Cup by 6m here a fortnight ago. The back row draws presents more of a challenge but he is going well enough to overcome it. MIGHTY RONALDO (9) produced some good results against strong company at the end of last campaign, placing in both the Bunbury and Governors cups and finishing fifth in the Nullarbor. Draws out and often needs a run to find form but his best form would measure right up. HOTLY PURSUED (5) is worth plenty of thought after coming from a wider barrier for a last-start win by 8 metres at this circuit and distance. SWEET PINS NZ (6) recorded back-to-back wins at this circuit and distance last month so is a player with his best form.",
